  "texts": [
    "This indicates that BIM and AI technologies like machine learning and natural language processing could be combined to further improve the efficiency and accuracy of the construction process.",
    "Zhou et al. (2022) suggested a novel cloud-based building fire alarm system utilizing BIM.",
    "It tackles the challenges of private data sharing and alignment of fire sensors in the BIM model.",
    "This suggests that AI technologies could be used to improve BIM's usability and interoperability, which could eventually result in increased safety and security in the CI.",
    "From the viewpoint of BIM-based project contractors in the Ma-laysian CI, Wan Mohammad et al. (2022) examined the significant uses of BIM, emphasizing the top BIM uses as 3D coordination and record model creation for facility management pur-poses."
